# Project Context

- Stack: Rust (Actix-web), PostgreSQL (SQLx), Docker Compose, Next.js

- Deployment: Docker containers managed via docker-compose.yml

- Compliance: DORA & EU AI Act project.



# Coding Standards

- Always use async/await in Rust.

- When fixing database issues, always check `migrations/` folder first.

- If editing Dockerfile, always propose a rebuild command.

- Backend: Vždy spustiť cargo check po každej väčšej zmene.

- Frontend: Vždy skontrolovať layout.tsx alebo sidebar, či je tam nový link.

- Databáza: Ak meníte DB, vždy skontrolovať priečinok migrations/, či pribudol nový súbor.



# Docker Instructions

- To restart DB: `docker-compose restart postgres`

- To view logs: `docker-compose logs -f veridion-nexus-api`

